Product name: Retro Alarm Clock, Antique Kienzle Desk Clock, Rustic Home Decor, Metal Metallic Rust, Antique Alarm Clock
Description:
Retro Alarm Clock, Antique Kienzle Desk Clock, Rustic Home Decor, Metal Metallic Rust, Antique Alarm Clock
This is a beautiful antique mechanical alarm clock with one alarm bell made by Kienzle in Germany. The clock must have been made circa 1920s.The clock has a great rustic feeling and plenty of patina, please examine the pictures for reference. One of the legs is not the clock's original (as you can see both legs are different). It does not fit properly, so it can be easily unscrewed but it will not fall off and the clock can still be displayed as normal.
The clock is currently in full working order, however with a clock this age I can not guarantee how long it will go on working. It would make a great home decor piece.
Measures approximately 5" (12.5 cm) in diameter around the widest back part.

In other traditions they can be benevolent or beneficent, bestowing boons or falling in love with humans. Mermaids have been a popular subject of art and literature and they have subsequently been depicted in operas, paintings, books, films and comics. 
Nymphs are a numerous class of lesser deities of mythology, conceived of as beautiful maidens inhabiting the sea, rivers, woods, trees, mountains, meadows, etc., and frequently mentioned as attending a superior deity.
